  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> You awaken in a damp cell, located in the deepest basement of the mysterious Waterfall Tower.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In making your way out, you discover you weren't the first in this predicament, someone preceded you - and they left behind hints that might help you abscond before the night is over.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A compact videogame experience that aims to evoke the classic, puzzle-centered adventure games of the past.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>             RIDDLES AND CONTRAPTIONS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a variety of puzzles and interact with the strange mechanisms that stand before you and the tower's exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>             THE KEY TO EGRESS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover and utilize a diverse set of items, essential in enabling your escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ed5b6c6617de5e034d6ada5c6376dfa5.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ed5b6c6617de5e034d6ada5c6376dfa5.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ed5b6c6617de5e034d6ada5c6376dfa5.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>             THE SECRETS OF WATERFALL TOWER</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exploring the tower and learning about the quirks of its strange inhabitants will be paramount to making progress. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/1e8825ce83f43ab4246e663b82752b87.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/1e8825ce83f43ab4246e663b82752b87.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/1e8825ce83f43ab4246e663b82752b87.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>             GARDEN OF SECRETS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New mysteries await after completing the game and unlocking the Epilogue. The adventure continues!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ccea33f7fd64d0d85ba5477f528059a6.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ccea33f7fd64d0d85ba5477f528059a6.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/ccea33f7fd64d0d85ba5477f528059a6.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i> You awaken in a damp cell, located in the deepest basement of the mysterious Waterfall Tower.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In making your way out, you discover you weren't the first in this predicament, someone preceded you - and they left behind hints that might help you abscond before the night is over.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A compact videogame experience that aims to evoke the classic, puzzle-centered adventure games of the past.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>             RIDDLES AND CONTRAPTIONS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/627d5ba5b620608d45e9bdd71cfe50c5.webp?t=1761331527\" width=500 height=22 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve a variety of puzzles and interact with the strange mechanisms that stand before you and the tower's exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.poster.avif?t=1761331527\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.webm?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2292710/extras/c1a639f06f8447078ff9321ed61ebbdd.mp4?t=1761331527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>             THE KEY TO EGRESS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.ak